.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
House: victorian, modern, tower, ranch-style
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, juice, tea
1. the japanese is the ranch-style house##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking 7up is the ranch-style house##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the modern house is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
9. the victorian house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| House         | modern      | ranch-style | victorian      | tower |
| Beverage     | soy-milk | 7up        | tea       | juice  |

