.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, fisherman, pilot, librarian
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, boat, subway
1. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person driving the scooter is the fisherman##1
4. the pilot is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the librarian is on the left of the fisherman##1
7. the librarian is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job    | pilot   | librarian      | fisherman       | videographer |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Transport     | subway     | jet-ski  | scooter | boat |

