.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, woodworking, reading, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, onion, orange, avocado
1. the person eating orange is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person eating onion is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person eating cranberry##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1
8. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby      | reading   | skydiving          | woodworking | singing        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Food           | cranberry | onion         | avocado         | orange |

