.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, musical, animation
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, scientist, social-worker
House: cape-cod, victorian, craftsman, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
2. the scientist is the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the social-worker is the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the craftsman house##1
5. the victorian house is between the journalist and the person watching zombie movies##2
6. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the scientist##3
7. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
8. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching musical movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | zombie      | musical       | animation    |
| Job           | librarian  | scientist  | social-worker | journalist |
| House   | farmhouse      | craftsman | victorian         | cape-cod    |

