.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, eggplant, kiwi, peas
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, canadian, german, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the turkish is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the turkish##3
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the turkish##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the turkish##1
7. the turkish is on the right of the person eating banana##1
8. the canadian is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
9. the egyptian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Food   | eggplant         | banana  | kiwi     | peas         |
| Nationality        | egyptian | canadian | turkish | german         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

