.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, indie, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, climbing, lacrosse, ice-hockey
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, swisher, dannemann, montecristo
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the fan of electronic and the fan of country##2
 5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the montecristo-smoker is the fan of indie##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is between the fan of punk and the fan of indie##2
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | indie    | electronic | punk    |
| Sport   | basketball | lacrosse | climbing  | ice-hockey |
| Cigar           | dannemann   | montecristo    | siglo        | swisher   |

