.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, poker, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, pop, disco, trance
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
7. the fan of pop is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Game           | scrabble | snooker | chess   | poker |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | r&b     | trance     | disco |

