.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, reading, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, hamster, cat
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the cat##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | reading    | puzzles  | traveling  | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Pet   | hamster    | chinchilla     | cat    | snake |

