.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, fantasy, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, davidoff, chaman, prince
1. the davidoff-smoker is between the person watching fantasy movies and the argentine##2
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the australian##1
5. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the turkish is between the chaman-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel | fantasy      | family  | satire    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Cigar           | prince      | chaman       | davidoff   | dunhill      |

