.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: go, snooker, billiard, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, animation, crime
1. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
2. the person playing snooker is between the person playing monopoly and the person watching comedy movies##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the japanese is between the person watching comedy movies and the australian##2
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | go    | billiard | snooker  | monopoly  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Movie-Genre         | animation   | comedy      | crime | fantasy       |

