.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, puzzles, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, ivory, purple, lavender
1. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes ivory is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby      | puzzles      | gardening | sudoku     | hiking    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Color           | purple   | ivory  | pink     | lavender |

