.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
City: miami, hamburg, paris, san-francisco
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, mechanic, doctor, librarian
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
3. the librarian is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the mechanic and the person traveling to paris##2
6. the entrepreneur is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| City       | paris   | miami | hamburg | san-francisco |
| Job   | librarian | doctor      | mechanic    | entrepreneur   |

