.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, grey, black, fuchsia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, spy, superhero
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia, tulip, begonia
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsrose is between the person who growszinnia and the person who likes fuchsia##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
4. the person who likes grey is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
7. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes fuchsia is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Color          | grey | fuchsia  | blue   | black    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | spy     | superhero | disaster |
| Flower   | tulip   | begonia | rose | zinnia   |

