.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, poker, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, may, august
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french, nigerian
1. the nigerian is in an even position##4
2. the canadian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person playing whist is the canadian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the french##1
7. the french is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | monopoly | scrabble | whist | poker   |
| Birthday   | june    | august   | may     | march    |
| Nationality   | dutch  | french | canadian  | nigerian |

