.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, mauve, blood-red, red
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, security-guard, social-worker
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, mouse, pony
1. the person who likes emerald is in an odd position##4
2. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the bartender##3
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes mauve is between the social-worker and the bartender##2
6. the electrician is on the left of the bartender##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Color    | blood-red    | mauve    | emerald  | red |
| Job   | social-worker | electrician | bartender | security-guard      |
| Pet     | horse   | bird        | pony   | mouse       |

 